How much does the UN cost YOU?

On average, taxpayers contribute USD 1.40 a year towards the UN budget.
@VisitUN tour guide Lisete explains. https://t.co/BtpTZEhzRY https://t.co/xcTp7zpA1t

Having a nationality is a fundamental human right. 

Yet, millions of people around the world are stateless. As a result, they often are not allowed to go to school, see a doctor or get a job.

@Refugees is helping: https://t.co/Nsc5mXv9oj #IBelong https://t.co/FoDJtY4WaB

For centuries, Lake Chad has been a source of life in the Sahel. Yet today, it has shrunk to 1/10th of its previous size.
@UNOCHA shares the images &amp; stories of those struggling to survive on its once vibrant shores.
